oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry Variety Show at the Huntsville Patton Street Armory
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Price, Ray, 1926-2013;Gibson, Don (Donald Eugene), 1928-2003;Brasfield, Rod
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) Hatch poster announcing the Grand Ole Opry Variety show featuring Rod Brasfield, Kitty wells, Flatt and Scruggs, Johnnie and jack, Don Gibson, and Ray Price at the Patton St. Armory on May 2. Poster features metal photoplates of Rod Brasfield, Kitty wells, Flatt and Scruggs, Johnnie and jack, Don Gibson, and Ray Price.
